702
00:32:16,250 --> 00:32:18,020
for web browsers and websites.

703
00:32:18,020 --> 00:32:21,060
And they're generally
2,048 bits long.

704
00:32:21,060 --> 00:32:23,840
That's seen as pretty secure.

