841
00:37:57,050 --> 00:37:58,500
which will be down here--

842
00:37:58,500 --> 00:38:03,320
R. I want 2P, for example.

843
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:05,870
Well, with 2P, I
can take a tangent

844
00:38:05,870 --> 00:38:07,460
and then find
where it intersects

845
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:09,450
and then go down
below the curve.

