909
00:40:49,310 --> 00:40:52,080
So from now on, lowercase
is regular number,

910
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:54,150
uppercase is point
on this curve,

911
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:58,678
or point on this mashed-up thing
