940
00:42:01,010 --> 00:42:02,480
And then error can accumulate.

941
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:06,470
And in a lot of cryptography,
you want zero error, right?

942
00:42:06,470 --> 00:42:09,500
Like in a hash function,
